[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/swords_dance">Swords Dance</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/swords_dance">Swords Dance</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>A frenetic dance to uplift the fighting spirit. It sharply raises the user's Attack stat.</p>